<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, June 21 (Xinhua) -- Executive Secretary of the
Commonwealth of Independent States (CIS) Boris Berezovsky said
Sunday that struggle against separatism is very acute at the
present time.
</P>
<P>
Berezovsky made the remark in Baku, capital of Azerbaijan, his
last leg of a three-nation tour, which already took him to Georgia,
Armenia.
</P>
<P>
