<HEADLINE> Malaysia's Anwar Reiterates Support for Mahathir </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, June 21 (Xinhua) -- The United Malays National
Organization (UMNO) deputy president Anwar Ibrahim Sunday
