the political and economic fields, ranging from the fight against
the proliferation of weapons of mass destruction, to the control
of the effects of the economic globalization by the government.
</P>
<P>
The French authorities pay tribute to the stabilizing role
played by China in the current economic turmoil in Asia,
particularly in relation with the efforts undertaken by the
Chinese authorities towards the modernization of the economy, he
said.
</P>
<P>
In this context, the fact that China has resisted the pressure
to devaluate its currency Renminbi is particularly remarkable, he
added. 
