commercial will also be aired in television live broadcast of these
games in addition to special fliers in the stada.
</P>
<P>
Ried added the image of the FIFA Fair Play logo will be seen on the
costumes of the match officials and on the armbands of the team
captains.
</P>
<P>
The referee will also flip a custom-made Fair Play coin before the
kick-off.
</P>
<P>
Before the game, players will all sign on the seven-point "good
conduct" charter drafted by French teenagers, she added. 
